#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:1
msgid "E4203"
msgstr "E4203"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `constr_as_function`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`constr_as_function`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:5
msgid ""
"MoonBit does not allow constructors to be passed directly as higher-order"
" functions. A constructor may still be called normally, but when a "
"function value is required, wrap the constructor call in a lambda so the "
"argument flow is explicit."
msgstr ""
"MoonBit 不允许将构造器直接作为高阶函数传递。构造器仍然可以正常调用，但在"
"需要函数值时，应使用 lambda 包装构造器调用，使参数传递过程保持明确。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:12
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv enum Message {\n"
"  Text(String)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn build(make : (String) -> Message) -> Message {\n"
"  make(\"ready\")\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let _ = build(Text)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:16
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:18
msgid "Use a lambda that calls the constructor."
msgstr "使用调用构造器的 lambda。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4203.md:20
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"priv enum Message {\n"
"  Text(String)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"fn build(make : (String) -> Message) -> Message {\n"
"  make(\"ready\")\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  let message = build(value => Text(value))\n"
"  match message {\n"
"    Text(value) => inspect(value, content=\"ready\")\n"
"  }\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

